    hadithEnglish:
      'Jabir (May Allah be pleased with him) reported:\nI heard the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) saying, The best way to celebrate the remembrance of Allah is to say: La ilaha illallah (there is no true god except Allah).\n\n[At-Tirmidhi].\n',
