      'Reported Amr bin Shuaib, on the authority of his father and grandfather that the Prophet (ﷺ) said, Do not pluck out grey hair, for they are the Muslims light on the Day of Resurrection.\n\n[Abu Dawud, At-Tirmidhi and An- Nasai].',
